the committee 
the principal items on bakers moscow agenda are accelerating 
arms control agreements seeking a solution to the war in 
afghanistan between the sovietbacked marxist government and 
usarmed moslem fundamentalist rebels and human rights 
we seek a more democratic soviet union where human rights 
gains are made permanent baker said 
