comments were made before the report of the cabinets resignation 
until a new government is formed the country will apparently be 
run by mladenov and a rubberstamp parliament 
atanassov a member of the communist party policymaking 
politburo became premier in march 1986 he survived the nov 10 
ouster of zhivkov apparently because he sided with the politburo 
colleagues who engineered the end of the authoritarian leaders 35 
years in power 
