nato was one of the conditions for german reunification but he 
left unclear whether it would also include the military integration 
into the alliance of what is now east germany walters made the 
remarks in a speech in stuttgart 
about twothirds of the 565000 soviet troops deployed in 
eastern europe are based in east germany 
likewise west germany is host to most of the 305000 us 
troops stationed in central europe to defend against a possible 
attack by the sovietled warsaw pact 
