forces down to 195000 for each superpower drew praise in both 
germanys 
kohl heralded the white house initiative as the right signal 
at the right time and said he considered the call for sharp 
reductions a pathmark to a new european security structure 
east germany also welcomed the proposal and expects it to help 
lead to an agreement at vienna arms talks to reduce conventional 
forces in europe government spokesman wolfgang meyer said 
