relatively little power compared with their comrades elsewhere in 
eastern europe the party is bolstered by roots in a century of the 
nations politics and relatively weak opposition 
however atanassov was not able to escape the shadow of zhivkov 
now under arrest on criminal charges or effectively deal with 
