5747 million a year earlier 
for the year the newspaper and information services company 
said its eanings from continuing operations rose to 1798 million 
or 343 a share up from 1468 million or 259 a share a year 
earlier the 1989 results include a gain of about 30 million from 
the sale of a pasadena calif newspaper 
