phelan announced thursday he would retire at the end of 1990 
after nearly seven years as chairman of the nations largest stock 
exchange 
he guided the exchange through a period of explosive growth 
championed new sophisticated technology and introduced 
controversial safeguards following the 1987 market crash and a 
nearrepeat performance in 1989 
